In re TYLER R. No. S231144. Supreme Court of California June 22, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 2/7. Review in the above captioned matter, which was granted and held for In re R.T., is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)

CORRIGAN, J., was absent and did not participate.
